                <p>We, the undersigned, having carefully examined the above described slaves of Mrs.
                        <persName>Eleanor R Lang</persName>, do appraise them respectfully, on the
                    amounts above named, set opposite their names</p>
                <closer>
               <signed><persName>Jackson Mitchell</persName></signed>
               <signed><persName>H. Addison</persName></signed>
            </closer>


