                <div2 type="section">
                    <p>I, <seg type="handwritten">
                     <persName>Eleanor R Lang</persName>
                  </seg> being
                        duly sworn, do depose and say, that all the several matters and things which
                        are set forth and stated in the foregoing petition, as of my own knowledge,
                        are true in substance and in fact; and that all the several other matters
                        and things therein set forth and stated, as from the information of others,
                        I believe to be true in substance and in fact.</p>
                    <closer> (Signed by) <signed>
                        <seg type="handwritten">her X mark <persName>Eleanor R Lang</persName></seg></signed></closer>
                    <closer><seg type="handwritten">Witness<lb/>
                        Sen <persName>Phi Thomas</persName></seg></closer>
